Summary for XSA

Provides the summary table used in ICES WG for XSA.

Generic Function

see See summary

Methods

object="FLXSA", stock="FLStock", R.age="character", Fbar.rng="character"
This will output a data.frame with the summary information. Note that the R.age and Fbar.rng arguments are necessary to compute extract R and compute Fbar
